# Product Surface

- Build a spectator-first mountain climbing race game, not a generic dashboard.
- Keep the core flow obvious: setup, start race, watch race, read result.
- Leaderboard, player progress, and race events should stay scannable at a glance.
- Make mobile usability a first-class constraint, then scale up for desktop.
- Keep the frontend ready to consume backend data without turning route payloads into UI-only shapes too early.
